    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior has several large dents, noticeable rust on the rocker panels, and the clear coat is peeling across the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission shifts harshly, indicating the need for immediate repairs. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car for someone willing to invest the time and resources into a full restoration.",
