    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable and stylish choice for your next adventure. It drives smoothly and looks great, showing only the minor signs of use you'd expect from a well-loved car. It's ready to provide many more miles of driving pleasure!",
